00108 void MSVehicleType::saveState(std::ostream& os) {
00109     FileHelpers::writeString(os, myID);
00110     FileHelpers::writeFloat(os, myLength);
00111     FileHelpers::writeFloat(os, myMinGap);
00112     FileHelpers::writeFloat(os, getMaxSpeed());
00113     FileHelpers::writeInt(os, (int) myVehicleClass);
00114     FileHelpers::writeInt(os, (int) myEmissionClass);
00115     FileHelpers::writeInt(os, (int) myShape);
00116     FileHelpers::writeFloat(os, myWidth);
00117     FileHelpers::writeFloat(os, myDefaultProbability);
00118     FileHelpers::writeFloat(os, mySpeedFactor);
00119     FileHelpers::writeFloat(os, mySpeedDev);
00120     FileHelpers::writeFloat(os, myColor.red());
00121     FileHelpers::writeFloat(os, myColor.green());
00122     FileHelpers::writeFloat(os, myColor.blue());
00123     FileHelpers::writeInt(os, myCarFollowModel->getModelID());
00124     FileHelpers::writeString(os, myLaneChangeModel);
00125     //myCarFollowModel->saveState(os);
00126 }

00209 SUMOReal MSVehicleType::get(const SUMOVTypeParameter::CFParams& from,
00210         SumoXMLAttr attr, SUMOReal defaultValue) {
00211     if (from.count(attr)) {

00218 MSVehicleType*
00219 MSVehicleType::build(SUMOVTypeParameter& from) {
00220     MSVehicleType* vtype = new MSVehicleType(from.id, from.length, from.minGap,
00221             from.maxSpeed, from.defaultProbability, from.speedFactor,
00222             from.speedDev, from.vehicleClass, from.emissionClass, from.width,
00223             from.shape, from.lcModel, from.color, from.mass, from.rolling_res,
00224             from.air_dens, from.frontal_area, from.drag_coefficient,
00225             from.Gear_ratio, from.Gear_sys_effc, from.regen_ratio,
00226             from.motor_sys_effc, from.cooper_losses, from.iron_losses,
00227             from.windage_losses, from.constant_losses, from.power_accs,
00228             from.num_cells, from.capacity, from.time_charge, from.celsius,
00229             from.humidity, from.aux_mask, from.light_mask,
00230             from.vehicle_headligths_consumption, from.front_fog_ligths_consumption,
00231             from.cockpit_ligths_consumption, from.radio_consumption,
00232             from.heatingAC_consumption);
00233 
00234     MSCFModel* model = 0;
00235     switch (from.cfModel) {
00236     case SUMO_TAG_CF_IDM:
00237         model = new MSCFModel_IDM(vtype,
00238                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_ACCEL, DEFAULT_VEH_ACCEL),
00239                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_DECEL, DEFAULT_VEH_DECEL),
00240                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_TAU, DEFAULT_VEH_TAU),
00241                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_CF_IDM_DELTA, 4.),
00242                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_CF_IDM_STEPPING, .25));
00243         break;
00244     case SUMO_TAG_CF_IDMM:
00245         model = new MSCFModel_IDM(vtype,
00246                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_ACCEL, DEFAULT_VEH_ACCEL),
00247                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_DECEL, DEFAULT_VEH_DECEL),
00248                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_TAU, DEFAULT_VEH_TAU),
00249                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_CF_IDMM_ADAPT_FACTOR, 1.8),
00250                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_CF_IDMM_ADAPT_TIME, 600.),
00251                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_CF_IDM_STEPPING, .25));
00252         break;
00253     case SUMO_TAG_CF_BKERNER:
00254         model = new MSCFModel_Kerner(vtype,
00255                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_ACCEL, DEFAULT_VEH_ACCEL),
00256                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_DECEL, DEFAULT_VEH_DECEL),
00257                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_TAU, DEFAULT_VEH_TAU),
00258                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_K, .5),
00259                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_CF_KERNER_PHI, 5.));
00260         break;
00261     case SUMO_TAG_CF_KRAUSS_ORIG1:
00262         model = new MSCFModel_KraussOrig1(vtype,
00263                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_ACCEL, DEFAULT_VEH_ACCEL),
00264                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_DECEL, DEFAULT_VEH_DECEL),
00265                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_SIGMA, DEFAULT_VEH_SIGMA),
00266                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_TAU, DEFAULT_VEH_TAU));
00267         break;
00268     case SUMO_TAG_CF_PWAGNER2009:
00269         model = new MSCFModel_PWag2009(vtype,
00270                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_ACCEL, DEFAULT_VEH_ACCEL),
00271                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_DECEL, DEFAULT_VEH_DECEL),
00272                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_SIGMA, DEFAULT_VEH_SIGMA),
00273                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_TAU, DEFAULT_VEH_TAU),
00274                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_CF_PWAGNER2009_TAULAST, 0.3),
00275                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_CF_PWAGNER2009_APPROB, 0.5));
00276         break;
00277     case SUMO_TAG_CF_WIEDEMANN:
00278         model = new MSCFModel_Wiedemann(vtype,
00279                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_ACCEL, DEFAULT_VEH_ACCEL),
00280                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_DECEL, DEFAULT_VEH_DECEL),
00281                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_CF_WIEDEMANN_SECURITY, 0.5),
00282                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_CF_WIEDEMANN_ESTIMATION, 0.5));
00283         break;
00284     case SUMO_TAG_CF_KRAUSS:
00285     default:
00286         model = new MSCFModel_Krauss(vtype,
00287                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_ACCEL, DEFAULT_VEH_ACCEL),
00288                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_DECEL, DEFAULT_VEH_DECEL),
00289                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_SIGMA, DEFAULT_VEH_SIGMA),
00290                 get(from.cfParameter, SUMO_ATTR_TAU, DEFAULT_VEH_TAU));
00291         break;
00292     }
00293     vtype->myCarFollowModel = model;
00294     return vtype;
00295 }

00297 MSVehicleType*
00298 MSVehicleType::build(const std::string& id, const MSVehicleType* from) {
00299     MSVehicleType* vtype = new MSVehicleType(id, from->myLength, from->myMinGap,
00300             from->myMaxSpeed, from->myDefaultProbability, from->mySpeedFactor,
00301             from->mySpeedDev, from->myVehicleClass, from->myEmissionClass,
00302             from->myWidth, from->myShape, from->myLaneChangeModel,
00303             from->myColor);
00304     vtype->myCarFollowModel = from->myCarFollowModel->duplicate(vtype);
00305     vtype->myOriginalType =
00306             from->myOriginalType != 0 ? from->myOriginalType : from;
00307     return vtype;
00308 }
